column5: opps.... We have to wait for TJ to get back from the pike fishing trip before we can announce the winners name. Today?...tonite?... please stay tuned!
Did i miss who the winner was?  If so...congrats on winning the Muskie Painting.  Thanks to Curtis Atwater/Extreme Angler TV and OFC for the contest.  FOTB
Ok, he's back, spill it  Maureen
The suspense is killing me....please pick me!!!!!!
i'm also curious who the lucky one was.  come on....spill the beans.  FOTB
Why do we have to wait till TJ gets back (he's already home)...did he win?
Just noticed this on the extemeanglertv.com website......    Congrats to Kyla Tooley on winning this awesome musky painting.  FOTB
Congrats Tyla!!!  That is one sweet painting!  Is she a member here?
That's a good question.  Maybe...maybe not.  I thought you had to be a member here in order to enter, but i could be wrong.  Either way congrats again to Kyla.  FOTB
